y}} | publisher={{le|Village Voice Media}} | access-date=2010-05-06 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100809160107/http://blogs.ocweekly.com/heardmentality/horrible-video-game-boxart---s/ | archive-date=2010-08-09 | url-status=yes | language=en }}</ref>评为史上最差游戏封面之一，不过欧洲地区的封面虽然也是真人，但是画面整体表现的元素与游戏吻合，且该封面也得到一些好评<ref>{{cite web |author1=Sophia Aubrey Drake |title=RetroVision – The Covers of Mega Man Part 3: Europe |url=http://ringsandcoins.com/retrovision-the-covers-of-mega-man-part-3-europe/ |website=Rings & Coins - 8 & 16-Bit Retro Gaming |accessdate=2021-09-04 |language=en |archive-date=2022-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220105060831/https://ringsandcoins.com/retrovision-the-covers-of-mega-man-part-3-europe/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author1=Defunct Games |title=USA vs. UK: Who Had the Best Mega Man Box Art? - Defunct Games |url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=419CSePS54M |website=YouTube |accessdate=2021-09-04 |archive-date=2022-01-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107011501/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=419CSePS54M |dead-url=no }}</ref>。被取消的作品《洛克人宇宙》中曾包括两个可玩角色，一个是经典的[[8位元|8位元]]洛克人，另一个则是该“糟糕封面”中的洛克人<ref>{{cite web | author=Spencer | date=2010-09-03 | title=There Are Three Mega Men In ''Mega Man Universe'' | url=http://www.siliconera.com/2010/09/03/there-are-three-mega-men-in-mega-man-universe/ | publisher=Siliconera | access-date=2011-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110106124032/http://www.siliconera.com/2010/09/03/there-are-three-mega-men-in-mega-man-universe/ | archive-date=2011-01-06 | url-status=dead|language=en }}</ref>。该封面中的洛克人在《[[快打旋風_X_鐵拳|快打旋風 X 鐵拳]]》中成为一位可操作角色<ref name="pac_mega">{{cite web|author=Pereira, Chris |date=2012-01-17 |title=Pac-Man, Mega Man Teased for ''Street Fighter X Tekken'' on Vita |url=http://www.1up.com/news/pac-man-mega-man-street-fighter-x-tekken |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120207064306/http://www.1up.com/news/pac-man-mega-man-street-fighter-x-tekken |url-status=dead |archive-date=2012-02-07 |publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |access-date=2012-03-10 }}</ref>。

=== 獎項 ===
本作在1990年的金摇杆奖中获得该年度“最佳8位家用机游戏奖”<ref name="Golden">{{cite journal|title=The Golden Joystick Awards '91|journal=[[电脑与电子游戏|电脑与电子游戏]]|issue=115|date=1991-06|page=10|publisher={{le|EMAP}}|url=https://archive.org/stream/Computer_Video_Games_Issue_115_1991-06_EMAP_Publishing_GB/Computer__Video_Games_Issue_115_1991-06_EMAP_Publishing_GB#page/n9/mode/1up|language=en}}</ref>。

各游戏杂志与网站授予了洛克人不同程度的荣誉。IGN将其列为“史上最佳100个红白机游戏”第30位<ref name="igntop" />，《[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]]》则在其1997年9月总100期中将该游戏列为“史上最佳100个任天堂游戏”第20位<ref>{{cite magazine | author=任天堂力量员工 | date=1997-09 | issue=100 | page=97 | title=Nintendo Power's 100 Best Nintendo Games of All Time | magazine=[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]] | publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂美国]] | issn=1041-9551 | url=https://readcomiconline.to/Comic/Nintendo-Power/Issue-100#104 | language=en | access-date=2021-09-04 | archive-date=2020-07-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200705200956/https://readcomiconline.to/Comic/Nintendo-Power/Issue-100#104 | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite magazine|date=2006-02| author=任天堂力量员工|title=NP Top 200| magazine=[[任天堂力量|任天堂力量]] | publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂美国]] | issue=200|pages=58–66 | issn=1041-9551|language=en}}</ref>。1UP.com将该游戏列为“被忽视的前5个游戏前传”之一以及“最佳25个红白机游戏“第17位<ref name="overlooked" /><ref>{{cite web|author=1UP员工 |title=The Top 25 NES Games |url=http://www.1up.com/features/top-25-nes-games?pager.offset=1 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110629043115/http://www.1up.com/features/top-25-nes-games?pager.offset=1 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2011-06-29 |work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |access-date=2010-03-17|language=en }}</ref>。英国杂志《{{le|游戏机器|The Games Machine}}》在其于PAL区发行后授予其“明星游戏”荣誉<ref name="gamesmachine" /><ref>{{cite news | author=Wee, Lim Choon | date=1990-10-18 | title=''Rockman'' goes to the rescue | newspaper={{le|新海峡时报|New Straits Times}} | publisher={{le|新海峡时报出版社|New Straits Times Press}} | page=15 | url=https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MKRUAAAAIBAJ&pg=5682,900843 | access-date=2010-05-04 | language=en | archive-date=2022-01-07 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220107011526/https://news.google.com/newspapers?id=MKRUAAAAIBAJ&pg=5682%2C900843 | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 回响 ==
本作在海外发行时鲜有报刊报道，当时《{{le|任天堂娱乐俱乐部新闻|Nintendo Fun Club News}}》为其开辟了一页专栏。游戏的销量通过玩家之间口口相传从而逐步积攒，使本作成为一部黑马作<ref name="TV" /><ref name="playmag" />。尽管该游戏于卡普空而言并不算商业上的大成功，但卡普空还是决定为其开发续作《[[洛克人2_威利博士之謎|洛克人2]]》，并于1988年在日本发行。由于新作跟进的敌人导致存储容量上的一些限制，《洛克人2》的设计元素多数来自前作<ref name="TV" /><ref>{{cite journal | journal=CFC Style Fan-Book | volume=3 | author=稻船敬二 | year=1997 | title=''Rockman'' 10th Anniversary Celebration Plans | publisher=[[卡普空|卡普空]] | language=ja | page=24 | author-link=稻船敬二}}</ref>。不过该续作在包装封面上有了重大改进，美国版本这次邀请了资深游戏插画师马克·埃里克森（Marc Eriksen）（曾为《出击飞龙》、《大蜜蜂》、《坏家伙》、《俄罗斯方块》、《钢铁帝国》、《脱狱 －战俘－》及《古巴战士》设计过封面）为其设计封面，但是却延续了“手枪”的错误。无论如何，该续作获得了巨大成功并奠定了洛克人系列在卡普空中的长寿地位<ref name="playmag" /><ref name="1upanniversary" />。由于“市场迫切的需求”，卡普空在1991年9月于美国地区重新发行了本作<ref name="gamepro">{{cite magazine | author=''GamePro'' staff|title=Game Boy ProView: ''Mega Man'' |magazine=[[GamePro|GamePro]] | issue=26 | page=68 | publisher=Infotainment World, Inc. |date=1991-09| issn=1042-8658|language=en}}</ref>。在该系列的后续五个作品中卡普空也依旧延续了8位风格及相同的精灵图。即使续作有着更为复杂的故事线，更多功能的游戏系统乃至更为优秀的游戏图形，洛克人游戏的核心元素却始终未变<ref name="steps" />，不过本作的得分系统没有延续到任何一部续作上<ref name="steps" />。

GamesRadar称洛克人为第一部带有“关卡选择”这种非线性游戏元素的游戏，与《[[超级马里奥兄弟|超级马里奥兄弟]]》及[[开放世界|开放世界游戏]]如《[[塞尔达传说|塞尔达传说]]》和《[[银河战士|银河战士]]》形成鲜明对比。网站亦将后来大多数游戏中的具有的非线性元素比如多任务、开放世界、繁重支线任务等归功于《洛克人》打下的基础<ref>{{cite web | author=GamesRadar 员工| date=2010-10-08 | title=Gaming's most important evolutions | url=http://www.gamesradar.com/f/gamings-most-important-evolutions/a-20101008102331322035/p-5 | work=[[GamesRadar|GamesRadar]] | publisher=[[未来出版社|未来出版社]] | access-date=2011-01-09|language=en}}</ref>。

=== 重制与再发行 ===
本作自1987年发售以来就被重新发行过多次。1994年卡普空于[[Mega_Drive|世嘉Mega Drive]]发行的游戏合集《[[洛克人極巨世界|洛克人極巨世界]]》包含了本作与第2、3部的图形及音乐加强版本<ref name="GameSpot history" />。1999年卡普空将本作移植到[[PlayStation_(遊戲機)|PlayStation]]上。并作为《{{le|洛克人大全集|Rockman Complete Works}}》的一部分在日本发售<ref name="completeworks" />。该版本不仅有重混音的音乐，更加入了“导航模式”，新增路标导航指引玩家前进<ref name="GameSpot history" /> 。在于北美地区发行的《{{le|洛克人纪念全集|Mega Man Anniversary Collection}}》中包含本作及其它九个系列游戏，卡普空于2004年在北美地区发行[[PlayStation_2|PlayStation 2]]及[[GameCube|GameCube]]版本，2005年发行[[Xbox_(游戏机)|Xbox]]版本<ref>{{cite web | author=Navarro, Alex | date=2004-06-21 | title=''Mega Man Anniversary Collection'' Review for PlayStation 2 | url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/mega-man-anniversary-collection-review/1900-6101043/ | work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | access-date=2015-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20040701032546/http://www.gamespot.com/ps2/action/megamananniversarycollection/review.html | archive-date= 2004-07-01 | url-status=live|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author=Navarro, Alex | date=2005-03-14 | title=''Mega Man Anniversary Collection'' Review for Xbox | url=http://www.gamespot.com/reviews/mega-man-anniversary-collection-review/1900-6120432/ | work=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]]| publisher=[[CBS_Interactive|CBS Interactive]] | access-date=2015-06-20 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20050321033403/http://www.gamespot.com/xbox/action/megamananniversarycollection/review.html | archive-date=2005-03-21 | url-status=live |language=en}}</ref>。由{{le|Lavastorm|Lavastorm Analytics}}开发供移动电话游玩的洛克人版本于2004年在北美发行并可供用户下载<ref name="mobile1" />。作为其分支，2007年在日本移动电话发行的版本于2008年得到了更新，玩家可以以萝露为主角进行游玩<ref name="mobile2" /><ref>{{cite web | author=Inside-Games staff | date=2008-04-04 | script-title=ja:カプコン、『ロックマン』『ロックマン2』を携帯3キャリア向けに完全移植+α | url=http://www.inside-games.jp/article/2008/04/04/28213.html | publisher=Inside-Games | language=ja | access-date=2010-05-09 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111003055101/http://www.inside-games.jp/article/2008/04/04/28213.html | archive-date=2011-10-03 | url-status=dead }}</ref>。2011年北京新艺互动于中国大陆发行了Java版本，名为《洛克人前传》。红白机版本的洛克人亦在[[Virtual_Console|Virtual Console]]在线商店重新发行并适配三种机型，[[Wii|Wii]]版本于2007年在欧洲发行，2008年在北美于日本发行<ref name="palvc">{{cite web | author=Spencer | date=2007-06-22 | title=Worldwide Virtual Console Outlook: ''Mega Man'' the Dolphin edition | url=http://www.siliconera.com/2007/06/22/worldwide-virtual-console-outlook-mega-man-the-dolphin-edition/ | publisher=Siliconera | access-date=2010-05-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121007054847/http://www.siliconera.com/2007/06/22/worldwide-virtual-console-outlook-mega-man-the-dolphin-edition/ | archive-date=2012-10-07 | url-status=live |language=en }}</ref><ref name="jpvc">{{cite web |first=JC |last=Fletcher |title=VC Tuesday: Rock! |url=http://nintendo.joystiq.com/2008/07/29/vc-tuesday-rock/ |work=[[Joystiq|Joystiq]] |publisher=[[AOL|AOL]] |date=2008-07-29 |access-date=2009-08-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120609110113/http://www.joystiq.com/2008/07/29/vc-tuesday-rock/ |archive-date=2012-06-09 |url-status=dead |language=en}}</ref><ref name="navc">{{cite news|author=任天堂员工|title=One WiiWare Game and Two Virtual Console Games Added to Wii Shop Channel|url=https://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/vJ7Uf4uCpcC79acvme0klnA1k9Siytm4|publisher=[[任天堂|任天堂美国]]|date=2008-08-18|access-date=2008-08-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080821043630/http://www.nintendo.com/whatsnew/detail/vJ7Uf4uCpcC79acvme0klnA1k9Siytm4|archive-date=2008-08-18|url-status=live|language=en}}</ref>，[[任天堂3DS|任天堂3DS]]版本于2012年发行，[[Wii_U|Wii U]]版本于2013年发行。《洛克人大全集》在北美与日本地区的[[PlayStation_Store|PlayStation Store]]亦有发售<ref name="jppsn">{{cite web | author=Spencer | date=2009-06-22 | title=''Mega Man Lands'' On PSN Game Archives Next Month | url=http://www.siliconera.com/2009/07/22/mega-man-lands-on-psn-game-archives-next-month/ | publisher=Siliconera | access-date=2010-05-05 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120810222756/http://www.siliconera.com/2009/07/22/mega-man-lands-on-psn-game-archives-next-month/ | archive-date=2012-08-10 | url-status=live|language=en }}</ref><ref name="napsn">{{cite web | author=Spencer | date=2011-01-18 | title=Import ''Mega Man'' Game Now On The US PlayStation Network | url=http://www.siliconera.com/2011/01/18/import-mega-man-game-now-on-the-us-playstation-store/ | publisher=Siliconera | access-date=2011-01-25 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110124054959/http://www.siliconera.com/2011/01/18/import-mega-man-game-now-on-the-us-playstation-store/ | archive-date=2011-01-24 | url-status=live |language=en }}</ref>。

本作亦有[[PlayStation_Portable|PlayStation Portable]]重制版《[[洛克人洛克人|洛克人洛克人]]》，于2006年在全球发行。本游戏在游戏图形上以三维[[Q版|Q版]]形式重制，人物亦改为二头身。根据[[稻船敬二|稻船敬二]]的描述，他本意是想将洛克人塑造为该造型，奈何因红白机机能所限而放弃<ref>{{cite web | author=Theobald, Phil | date=2005-09-17 | title=''Mega Man'' on PSP -- Keiji Inafune and Tatsuya Kitabayashi Interview | url=http://ps2.gamespy.com/articles/651/651835p1.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329111321/http://ps2.gamespy.com/articles/651/651835p1.html |archive-date=2012-03-29 | work=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]| publisher=IGN | access-date=2010-05-08|language=en}}</ref>，制作人北林达也表示重塑人物造型是由于PlayStation Portable屏幕比例为16:9而导致的。人物的大头造型使得开发小组可以塑造不同的面部表情<ref name="gamespy2">{{cite web | author=McGarvey, Sterling | date=2006-02-24 | title=Tetsuya Kitabayashi Discusses the Mega-Makeover (PSP) | url=http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-portable/rockman-rockman/691350p1.html |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120329113315/http://ps2.gamespy.com/playstation-portable/rockman-rockman/691350p1.html |archive-date=2012-03-29| work=[[GameSpy|GameSpy]]| publisher=IGN | access-date=2011-03-22|language=en}}</ref>。人物设计师吉川达哉解释道：“这种设计的理念源于‘玩具’，我们想要围绕小朋友来塑造可爱的设计。就像那些平常见到在钥匙扣上挂着的那些人物，不仅如此，我也让设计师确保洛克人原作中的细节不被丢失，我们想要在这些设计上也能准确展现出他们的比例与运动。”<ref name="r203">{{cite book|isbn=978-1-897376-79-9 |date=2010-01-06|title=Mega Man: Official Complete Works|publisher={{le|Udon Entertainment}} | pages=108–13|language=en}}</ref>由于重制版的关卡比例与原作不同，使得开发者可以利用宽屏中的更多空间<ref name="gamespy2" />。不过本作的零售版本销量欠佳，后期于日本[[PlayStation_Network|PlayStation Network]]在线商店以付费下载形式发售<ref name="r203" /><ref>{{cite web|author=Parish, Jeremy |date=2007-05-31 |title=Mega Manniversary: Mega Morrow |url=http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3159950 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20070729174553/http://www.1up.com/do/feature?cId=3159950 |url-status=dead |archive-date=2007-07-29 |work=[[1UP.com|1UP.com]] |publisher=[[Ziff_Davis|Ziff Davis]] |access-date=2010-05-09}}</ref><ref>{{cite web | author=Fami通员工 | date=2009-12-15 | title=『ロックマン』シリーズ4作品がPlayStation Storeで配信決定 | url=http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1230524_1124.html | work=[[Fami通|Fami通]] | publisher=[[Enterbrain|Enterbrain]] | language=ja | access-date=2010-05-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023010414/http://www.famitsu.com/game/news/1230524_1124.html | archive-date=2012-10-23| url-status=live }}</ref>，2008年卡普空亦将该作翻译为中文版本以在亚洲地区发行<ref>{{cite web | author=Spencer | date=2008-04-23 | title=Mega Man powers up… learns Chinese? | url=http://www.siliconera.com/2008/04/23/mega-man-powers-up%E2%80%A6-learns-chinese/ | publisher=Siliconera | access-date=2010-05-31 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20091201170627/http://www.siliconera.com/2008/04/23/mega-man-powers-up%E2%80%A6-learns-chinese/ | archive-date=2009-12-01 | url-status=dead |language=en}}</ref>。

